attributes.Long form description: First, the student assembles the two Joy-Cons into the comfort grip. Next, the student attaches both Joy-Cons to the Nintendo Switch console with the instructor's help. Then, the student removes the Joy-Cons and then assembles then into the Joy-Con straps. After that, the student stands the Nintendo Switch Console on the table using the kickstand. Then, the student exchanges the game card. After that, the student exchanges the SD card. Lastly, the student turns on the Nintendo Switch.
